text: "What Was I Made For?" is a song by American singer Billie Eilish from Barbie: The Album, the soundtrack of the movie Barbie. The song was released through Atlantic Records, Darkroom and Interscope Records on July 13, 2023. The song was later released to Italian radio on July 17, 2023. It won the Academy Award for Best Original Song at the 96th Academy Awards. It was nominated for five awards at the 66th Annual Grammy Awards, including Record of the Year. The song eventually won Song of the Year. ==References== Category:2023 songs Category:Billie Eilish songs Category:Best Original Song Academy Award-winning songs
